list.name: Default
list.comment: -fixed some autorization issues -added add button to nav and moved logout button to top when user is logged in -fixed issue with updating games -only users with admin permissions can access the edit button for games

task.summary: Default task

-Added images from hgame site for each game -got dynamic content loading properly with ajax -added db connection and tested that it works with selecting from the games table -initial style of the website has made great progress
Testing update of modal button classes
-Removed loading container -Tweaked modal button styles

-Added search filter and re-organized files to have includes with relative paths for each page. -Styled search field and other small style adjustments -consolidated script and css includes to be in separate files as well as created header and footer files for including on each page.

-Added favoriting ability for users who are logged in -added ability to edit games -created plus button on favorites page to add more games... thinking of where else to put an "add game" button since that is the main purpose of the web app

-fixed some autorization issues -added add button to nav and moved logout button to top when user is logged in -fixed issue with updating games -only users with admin permissions can access the edit button for games

-Added multi level auth deleting/un-approving of games using different authenticatino levels (Super, Admin, and User) -Took out big buttons unless logged in -Moved login and join buttons to top of page -Added animations when deleting or un-favoriting a game
-Fixed issue with search bar and top nav overlapping when scrolled down -fixed z-index issue with image upload modal -other minor style adjustments

-fixed some autorization issues -added add button to nav and moved logout button to top when user is logged in -fixed issue with updating games -only users with admin permissions can access the edit button for games -fixed authentication issues
-fixed issue where go button on search wouldn't work

-Did search engine optimization (sitemap and robots/urllist .txt files) -varified site to google webmaster and submitted sitemap -added apple touch and fav icons -added facebook commenting and like/sharing for each game that goes on the site -adjusted style of game embed tags to have blue border

-fixed issue where game scraping wouldn't work with miniclip --now it uses the proxy to display the game but then when the game is added it adds the correct url (uses unproxify url function in unproxify-url.php page) -changed game scraper to search for elements that have an attribute of data-src

-fixed some autorization issues -added add button to nav and moved logout button to top when user is logged in -fixed issue with updating games -only users with admin permissions can access the edit button for games
-provided some extra direction on the add game page to make it more clear that it will find flash games on any website
-added full screen feature for all games
-added edit button to the play page for admins
-fixed share buttons for small screens
-added page for mygames demo that will be shown on first login and to non-users at un-determined time/placement as of current
-fixed issue with login not working properly -demo page is displayed if the user doesn't have any favorite games... also accessible via the top menu
-added automatic scroll on play page -adjusted facebook sharing widget to be with comment widget and moved flash game up on page
-added bootstrap 3.2.0 to the project
